{"tid":768102,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人試過人地生日就要奉旨夾錢送禮物，自己生日就連一句祝福都無","createTime":"2018-08-05T06:06:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-05T06:37:23.000Z","uid":172116,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"01b814e33230f1f1633fdbe19b960bcf14688bd9","tid":768102,"uid":172116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T06:06:25.000Z","msg":"今年9月讀yr 4, 有班小圈子frds,<br />\n每年圈入面有人生日，就要奉旨諗送咩，仲要夾錢送生日禮物。仲要精挑細選，陪人買生日禮物，仲要係每份禮物都幾百蚊，有次仲要親手diy cake。但今日係我生日，竟然圈入面無一個人同我講生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n識佢地既頭一年送咗盞爛既燈俾我，一睇就知係淘寶貨，實係運嚟時整爛咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個年話請我去圈子入面是但一個人既屋企過生日，嗰度仲好遠，喺元朗，而我係住九龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過心諗算啦！見佢地都有心，但我6點放工去到時，佢地打嚟話出去買蛋糕同壽司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我喺後樓梯等咗個幾鐘，佢地先返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連個蛋糕都係超唔新鮮嗰隻。梗係啦！成6點幾先出去買蛋糕，新鮮極有限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n都最尾我收到盞爛燈作生日禮物後，嬲嬲地dum咗入垃圾桶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 發誓以後唔會再去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為同做show無分別。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後嗰幾年，佢地都無再同我慶祝生日，而每次佢地生日都總係要我出錢又出力，我以為我對人好，佢地總有一日會感受到，對返我好，結果係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到今年連一句祝福到無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我真係唔想下年再出錢出力幫佢地慶祝生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  連祝福都懶得再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我既故事話俾大家知，唔好以為你對人好，人地就會對返你好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有啲人係以為人地奉旨對佢好。"},{"pid":"8ae7f3735621e335e39f42e5aa933a0cf4f9252e","tid":768102,"uid":21432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T06:10:58.000Z","msg":"咁咪識過第二班人，咁都要打一大篇野？"},{"pid":"04cfe2f12436cd7d16665502076991f37b4512fe","tid":768102,"uid":147916,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T06:27:20.000Z","msg":"i know ur feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最深刻係有個臭閪 佢連續兩年生日我就好俾心機揀禮物比佢<br />\n我生日佢就送啲垃圾俾我  第二年直頭無件事<br />\n睇佢story又同其他frd夾錢送勁貴嘅波鞋比人做生日禮物"},{"pid":"5b014c839e672a2ebfb47b178511f1bd149e7a87","tid":768102,"uid":172116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04cfe2f12436cd7d16665502076991f37b4512fe","tid":768102,"uid":147916,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T06:27:20.000Z","msg":"i know ur feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最深刻係有個臭閪 佢連續兩年生日我就好俾心機揀禮物比佢<br />\n我生日佢就送啲垃圾俾我  第二年直頭無件事<br />\n睇佢story又同其他frd夾錢送勁貴嘅波鞋比人做生日禮物"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T06:37:23.000Z","msg":"u really know my feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  覺得自己都幾白痴，咁俾心機同人慶生，就連一句祝福都無，即係連戲都唔肯交出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}